org.gearvrf.script.javascript

Class GVRJavascriptV8File

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gearvrf.script.javascript.GVRJavascriptV8File

  • public class GVRJavascriptV8File
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a Javascript file that will be compiled and run by the V8 engine Once a script text is set or loaded, you can invoke functions in the script using nvokeFunction(String functionName, Object[] parameters)}, to handle events delivered to it.
